Common questions
Is WeedStop really free?
Yes, 100% free forever. No subscriptions, no hidden costs, no credit card required. Every feature is completely accessible from day one.
Is my data private?
Absolutely. WeedStop is fully anonymous â€” no real name, no email verification, no data selling. Your recovery journey stays between you and the app.
What platforms is WeedStop available on?
WeedStop is currently available for Android devices. iOS support is planned for the future.
Can WeedStop replace professional treatment?
No. WeedStop is a supportive tool, not a medical treatment. It's designed to complement professional help, not replace it. If you're struggling with severe addiction, please consult a healthcare professional.
How do the global leaderboards work?
Each mini-game has its own global leaderboard. Your highscores are ranked against all WeedStop users worldwide. It's completely anonymous â€” only your chosen username is visible.
How do I contact the team?
Email us at stylixweedstop@gmail.com. We read and respond to every message.
